description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking to expand your skills and enhance your career to include providing Complex Clinical Care or do you already have Complex Care experience? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apollo Home Healthcare is seeking an experienced Support Worker to support a lady with complex care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for dedicated and compassionate Support workers who are passionate about their job, enjoy delivering one to one support and who can build positive relationships with our service users and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our service user is looking for a committed Health Care Assistant to support her throughout the day to ensure sure she is comfortable and support with her needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;She enjoys watching films, listening to music, being read too and loves spending time with family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity to make a difference to this lady’s everyday life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• 6 months of previous care experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Medication Administration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Personal Care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Moving and Handling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Gastrostomy Care (Peg Feeding)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have the following shifts available;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;• Day shifts from 8am to 9pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a personally rewarding role where you can build on your clinical skills and experience, whilst delivering exceptional care and support to our service user and really making an impact on her day to day life.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why work for Apollo Home Healthcare?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in the provision of highly complex clinical care services delivered in the homes of service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are passionate about delivering the highest standard of care and we recognise that our Nurses, Healthcare Assistants and Support Workers are integral to doing this. In return for your hard work and dedication you will receive:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible hours to suit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmed rotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent rates of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holiday pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full clinical training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work with other service users in the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing professional training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need key workers on the front line supporting our service users in the fight against the COVID-19 Pandemic.&lt;/p&gt;
